<br>
Assist key:<br>
/assist tank<br>
/stopsong<br>
/pause 2<br>
/pet attack<br>
/cast #<br>
<br>
this would give me main assist capability<br>
this would send my pet in to MA the tank.<br>
this would stop whatever song I was playing, and would start a new song.<br>
<br>
I usually use the first song in my lineup for that group as the song # in the /cast line.<br>
<br>
seems to work, but it takes a bit getting used to not twisting right after assisting, since a song is started.<br>
